  "character_name": "林路",
  "comments": [],
  "completed": false,
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "那个，你好，请问您就是林路先生吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是，请说。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "太好啦！我没有找错人！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "您好，我是zero，是林阿姨介绍过来的！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我找你是因为",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "啧。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "不好意思啊，我没有结婚的打算，我这辈子都不会结婚的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？哦哦，好的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我妈那边，我会说的，不好意思，耽误你了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "那个，林先生，您是不是误会了点什么啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是过来和你相亲的，我是过来请教你一些问题的！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "您误会我了！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "咳咳，不好意思，最近母亲催的实在是有点紧。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我明明都说过了，我不想结婚。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是他们没有一个人把我的话放在心里。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "哎呀，没事没事，这种事情，很正常的啦~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    }
  ],
